{"tid":299133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這如果是男醫師，還有辦法問診嗎","createTime":"2017-06-26T23:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T02:39:35.000Z","uid":81228,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3643b0000f1f318f4d57de62373e26ff3adab8ed","tid":299133,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T23:30:45.000Z","msg":"近日有網友在PTT表特版PO出一張照片，照片中醫院裡一名正妹正在喝水，高顏值+傲人上圍超吸睛，讓網友大呼：「這如果是男醫師，還有辦法問診嗎XDD」。<br />\n<br />\n真的超正的！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.yes-news.com/yespick/201706/PmkdwBlQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.yes-news.com%2Fyespick%2F201706%2FPmkdwBlQ.jpg&h=612ad243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友紛紛留言「我不想當人了，我要當水瓶」、「以為是SOD，原來是看醫生啊」、「聽診器不知道怎麼擺」、「感覺快滑下來了」、「喝的很兇」 。<br />\n<br />\n他偷拍超兇正妹看病喝水，網友暴動：「男醫師能專心問診嗎？」！<br />\n<br />\n據悉，這名正妹名叫姚採辰，是表特版常客，目前的職業是全職Show Girl。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.yes-news.com/yespick/201706/6RY3oZHT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.yes-news.com%2Fyespick%2F201706%2F6RY3oZHT.jpg&h=64db61ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.yes-news.com/yespick/201706/ppiLduwO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.yes-news.com%2Fyespick%2F201706%2FppiLduwO.jpg&h=bc597c99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來欣賞更多美照吧~<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.yes-news.com/yespick/201706/2xEhwgGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.yes-news.com%2Fyespick%2F201706%2F2xEhwgGm.jpg&h=5ea3ec2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他偷拍超兇正妹看病喝水，網友暴動：「男醫師能專心問診嗎？」！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.yes-news.com/yespick/201706/C1A9CVZJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.yes-news.com%2Fyespick%2F201706%2FC1A9CVZJ.jpg&h=d83286dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.yes-news.com/yespick/201706/NYMbXt5m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.yes-news.com%2Fyespick%2F201706%2FNYMbXt5m.jpg&h=fafd976f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.